node.text:
My upcoming variant incentive cover to🔺Bermuda🔻 #2 has been revealed! This is a fun new creator owned book drawn by @nkwbradshaw and written by John Layman and is in stores Aug 18 through @idwpublishing 

Colors by @sabine_rich . I had fun working in the triangle and crop-circle design motifs into my layout and echoing the pose to fit that same triangular shape. It’s fun to occasionally still do more unusual new ideas and characters. 

#bermuda #bermudatriangle #jscottcampbell #drawing #comicbooks #art #comicbookart #idw #idwcomics #adventure
